Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:36.94,Default1,,0,0,0,,霍克斯 个性 刚翼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.84,Default1,,0,0,0,,魃宁 个性 燃发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:43.10,Default1,,0,0,0,,爆豪胜己 个性 爆破
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:46.56,Default1,,0,0,0,,绿谷出久 个性 One for all
